### SIGA Gateway API - Testing Guide

## Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json

## ====== HEALTH CHECK ======

### Check Overall Gateway Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Check User Service Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/UserService

### Check Order Service Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/OrderService

### Check Delivery Service Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/DeliveryService

## ====== USERS ======

### Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a1

### Get User by Email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/email/joao.silva@email.com

### Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
  "phone": "31999999999",
  "role": "customer"
}

### Update User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
  "phone": "31999999999",
  "role": "customer"
}

### Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a1

## ====== ORDERS ======

### Get All Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders

### Get Order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a3

### Create Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a2",
  "customerId": "65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a1",
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Mouse Gamer",
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "name": "Teclado Mecânico",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "status": "processing"
}

### Update Order
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a3
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "shipped"
}

### Delete Order
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a3

## ====== DELIVERIES ======

### Get All Deliveries
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliveries

### Get Delivery by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/deliveries/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a4

### Create Delivery
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/deliveries
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderId": "65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a3",
  "courierId": "65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a5",
  "status": "pending",
  "pickupAddress": {
    "street": "Av. Brasil, 1000",
    "city": "Belo Horizonte",
    "state": "MG"
  },
  "deliveryAddress": {
    "street": "Rua das Flores, 200",
    "city": "Contagem",
    "state": "MG"
  },
  "estimatedDelivery": "2026-03-07T18:00:00Z"
}

### Update Delivery
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/deliveries/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a4
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_TRANSIT"
}

### Delete Delivery
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/deliveries/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a4

## ====== DELIVERY EVENTS ======

### Get All Delivery Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery-events

### Get Delivery Event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery-events/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a6

### Get Events by Delivery ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery-events/delivery/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a4

### Get Events by Order ID (Delivery History)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery-events/order/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a3

### Get Latest Status of Delivery
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery-events/latest/65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a4

### Create Delivery Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/delivery-events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "deliveryId": "65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a4",
  "orderId": "65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a3",
  "eventType": "OUT_FOR_DELIVERY",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-07T15:00:00Z",
  "actor": {
    "type": "courier",
    "id": "65f7e1bbf9b2a4f1a9c38b9a5"
  }
}

## ====== SCALAR & AGGREGATOR ======

### Open Scalar UI (abra no navegador)
GET {{baseUrl}}/scalar/

### List aggregator services
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/swagger/services

### Get aggregated specs (JSON por serviço)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/swagger/specs
